medicinemanagements

Class ReplenishmentRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • medicinemanagements.ReplenishmentRequest

  • public class ReplenishmentRequest
extends java.lang.Object
    The ReplenishmentRequest class represents a request to replenish stock for a specific medicine. It contains details about the medicine, the requested stock quantity, the requester, and the request status.

    • Constructor Detail

      • ReplenishmentRequest

        public ReplenishmentRequest(java.lang.String medicineName,
                            int requestedStock,
                            java.lang.String requestBy,
                            java.lang.Boolean isNewMedicine)
        Constructs a ReplenishmentRequest with the specified medicine name, requested stock quantity, requester, and whether the medicine is new. The request status is set to PENDING by default.
        Parameters:
        medicineName - The name of the medicine to be replenished.
        requestedStock - The quantity of stock being requested.
        requestBy - The ID or name of the requester.
        isNewMedicine - true if the request is for a new medicine, false otherwise.
